            "name_id": 0xa,
            "extra_id": 0x1a0,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x0,
            "msg_string": "Thank you for your business, Ayesha.<CR>Alllsssooo...!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xa,
            "name_id": 0xa,
            "extra_id": 0x69,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "I saw that. Who was that man who came to visit you? How do you know him?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15a,
            "expr_id": 0x5,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "Umm, what man?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xa,
            "name_id": 0xa,
            "extra_id": 0x6b,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "That man with a mustache. He was a very splendid gentleman."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15b,
            "expr_id": 0x5,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "A mustache... Oh, do you mean Mr. Harry?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xa,
            "name_id": 0xa,
            "extra_id": 0xfd,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "Umm, I hope you were just joking. You know, that ruggedly handsome gentleman?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x160,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "Ruggedly handsome...? Ohh!<CR>Are you talking about Mr. Keith?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "Umm, it's hard to explain, but I guess we work in the same field."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xa,
            "name_id": 0xa,
            "extra_id": 0x15e,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "Oh, so he's an apothecary too? I see..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xa,
            "name_id": 0xa,
            "extra_id": 0x160,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "msg_string": "No wonder he looked so composed and intellectual. Yup, yup, he's amazing."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x7,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "msg_string": "Marietta, could you be...<CR>Do you like men like him?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xa,
            "name_id": 0xa,
            "extra_id": 0x1a7,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xb,
            "msg_string": "Stop that! I didn't mean it that way."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xa,
            "name_id": 0xa,
            "extra_id": 0x69,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0xc,
            "msg_string": "...But, if that gentleman were to approach me, I don't think I could say no."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xd,
            "msg_string": "Umm, but he's a lot older than you..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xa,
            "name_id": 0xa,
            "extra_id": 0x6a,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0xe,
            "msg_string": "That's lovely, too. He has a calmness and economic strength that you can't find in guys around my age."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xa,
            "name_id": 0xa,
            "extra_id": 0x6b,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xf,
            "msg_string": "Goodness, both of them having mustaches, I wonder how they can be so different..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xa,
            "name_id": 0xa,
            "extra_id": 0xf5,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x10,
            "msg_string": "I wish the owner would act more composed, like that gentleman."
        }
    ]
}